# IVR Management Dashboard - Warp Configuration

## Project Overview
A comprehensive web application for managing and configuring Interactive Voice Response (IVR) routing systems. Built with React 18, TypeScript, Vite, and modern UI libraries.

## Technology Stack
- **Framework**: React 18.3.1 with TypeScript
- **Build Tool**: Vite 6.3.5
- **Package Manager**: pnpm
- **Routing**: React Router DOM v7.11.0
- **UI Components**: Radix UI (shadcn/ui), Material-UI
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4.1.12
- **Charts**: Recharts 2.15.2
- **Flow Diagrams**: @xyflow/react 12.10.0
- **Notifications**: Sonner 2.0.3
- **Forms**: React Hook Form 7.55.0

## Key Features
- Dashboard with real-time call monitoring and system health
- Routing management with advanced search and filtering
- Segment configuration (Menu, Say, Scheduler, Recognize, Queue, Collect)
- Message library (audio files + TTS)
- Visual segment flow editor with drag-and-drop
- Administration panel with audit logging

